### Send OTP (Initial login request)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/portal/loginCheck
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.johnson@company.com"
}

### Resend OTP (wait at least 30 sec between resends)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/portal/loginCheck
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.johnson@company.com",
  "action": "resend"
}

### Verify OTP and login (replace 123456 with actual OTP received via email)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/portal/loginCheck
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.johnson@company.com",
  "otp": "324315"
}
